{"title":"跋涉","authors":["冷慰怀"],"dates":[{"year":1988,"month":10,"day":13}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"跋涉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冷慰怀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真想成为一首诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让每个日子都读出韵律"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春雨霏霏时"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"邀几位朋友走入意境"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与那个年过千岁的牧童"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共访杏花村沉醉的旧址"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而命运专爱同我们作对"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"失望如魔鬼纠缠不休"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一封信盼了很久"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捧在手里却不敢启封"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生怕退稿笺又来扳着面孔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"重复那些冰冷的训词"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炒菜老忘放盐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烧饭总是糊底"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"急急去赴约会"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又偏偏赶上一场暴雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"背得烂熟的箴言"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"竟然不知道出在何处！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过了三十岁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们才渐渐懂得——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在生活这首诗里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灵感  并非全是警句"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}